claim: UPDATED. Provocation and Disinformation Overview
FAKE: In Ukraine, the theft and homicide levels rose due to power outages
MANIPULATION: Ukrainians beat two Berlin residents for speaking in russian
FAKE: A quote from Paul Goebbels about the Banderites
FAKE: The “Culture of good neighborliness” course for Ukrainian schoolchildren promotes gender and sexual orientation change
FAKE: US research in Ukraine led to an increase in the incidence of tick-borne borreliosis in Ukraine and an increase in the number of ticks in russia
FAKE: In Chile, the law on the rights of “mutants” and genetically modified people has been approved – Ostap Stakhiv
FALSE: The COVID-19 incidence rate became zero in late May 2022
FAKE: The risk of death among children vaccinated against COVID-19 is 52 times greater, says ONS
